---
title: Southwestern Tortellini Salad with Black Beans, Sweet Corn, and Cilantro
description: Get ready for a Southwestern twist on pasta salad! This warm salad is full of beans, cilantro, corn, and chili flakes for a very unique spin. Cheese-filled tortellini are a major upgrade from regular old pasta.
